title: Migos Go Full Rockstar in New “What the Price” Video
text:
Migos Go Full Rockstar in New “What the Price” Video Never mind the bollocks, here’s the Sex Beatles. 
Fully buying into the ever-growing trap-artists-as-rockstars aesthetic, Migos have released their new video for "What the Price." It sees Quavo, Takeoff, and Offset decked out in denim, leather and bandanas, guitars strapped around their necks, jumped up on vodka. There's also liberal use of yellow CAUTION tape and a fucking terrific slo-mo bar fight with some mean-mugging biker types. 
Watch the whole video below and air guitar the shit out of the rest of your day.
